{"tid":1245183,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"球王美斯用一場波打到c朗拿度球迷口腫面腫。","createTime":"2019-06-20T08:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T09:00:02.000Z","uid":43785,"like":16,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b570333b06c6dce39489f76b9476d0921b886c","tid":1245183,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:01:39.000Z","msg":"1,順境球王？<br />\nc朗拿度球迷成日用順境球王嚟串我球王美斯， 事實上球王美斯啱啱入咗一球逆境波。<br />\n<br />\n2, 球王美斯唔識射12碼？<br />\n邊個話佢唔識踢12碼， 今場踢咗一球好靚嘅12碼，直射入網。<br />\n<br />\n3,友誼賽球王真正比賽唔識入波？<br />\n邊個話真正比賽唔識入波今日美斯就係入咗一球，救國呀。<br />\n<br />\n4，依賴巴塞體系？<br />\n今場對巴拉圭，表現出色，有入波，擺脫左巴塞體制。可見美斯將自己融入左阿根廷既踢法。<br />\n<br />\n5，小組賽出局？<br />\n出乜野局？今次全靠美斯實力追返一球。<br />\n下場對卡塔爾呢隊垃圾，贏埋就可以穩入8強，到時就再洗過牌，美斯個夢想仍然有可能實現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n估唔到美斯咁勁，只係一場波就可以將民情逆轉，<br />\n朗迷被球王美斯用實力打面，顛覆晒平時講既野<br />\n你地仲有乜野好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56489a6a76a2e6b4664f2f7504f6ae0b8648b37","tid":1245183,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />朗迷"},{"pid":"c0e588ede9daef520694b1292a9d9559cfe09de9","tid":1245183,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:15:53.000Z","msg":"如果下場和波？"},{"pid":"c3d9442d33829066f049e1a4159481ddc0f9b174","tid":1245183,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:18:47.000Z","msg":"曲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18601e4bc6c2eca3d279eef931e28bfadcd4d46e","tid":1245183,"uid":43785,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c0e588ede9daef520694b1292a9d9559cfe09de9","tid":1245183,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c